BreadfundsUnit::initialize
├── when already initialized
│   └── it reverts
└── when not initialized
    └── it sets the owner correctly

BreadfundsUnit::setTokenAllowed
├── when caller is not owner
│   └── it reverts
└── when caller is owner
    ├── when setting token to allowed
    │   ├── it updates the token status to true
    │   └── it emits TokenAllowed event with true
    └── when setting token to not allowed
        ├── it updates the token status to false
        └── it emits TokenAllowed event with false

BreadfundsUnit::create
├── when breadfund already exists
│   └── it reverts with AlreadyExists
├── when token is not allowed
│   └── it reverts with TokenNotAllowed
├── when breadfund start time is zero
│   └── it reverts with InvalidBreadfundStartTime
├── when owner is zero address
│   └── it reverts with InvalidOwner
├── when initial deposit is zero or less
│   └── it reverts with InvalidInitialDeposit
├── when fixed deposit is zero or less
│   └── it reverts with InvalidFixedDeposit
├── when auto threshold is zero or less
│   └── it reverts with InvalidThreshold
├── when minimum members is less than two
│   └── it reverts with InvalidMinimumMembers
├── when maximum members is less than minimum members
│   └── it reverts with InvalidMaximumMembers
├── when epoch duration is zero
│   └── it reverts with InvalidEpochDuration
├── when small withdraws limit is zero
│   └── it reverts with InvalidSmallWithdrawsLimit
├── when member address is zero
│   └── it reverts with InvalidMemberAddress
├── when members array is empty
│   └── it processes with no members
├── when members array has duplicates
│   └── it sets member status correctly for duplicates
├── when members count exceeds maximum members
│   └── it processes all members
├── when consensus threshold is zero
│   └── it creates breadfund with zero threshold
├── when consensus threshold is 100
│   └── it creates breadfund requiring unanimous consent
├── when ratio is zero
│   └── it creates breadfund with zero ratio
└── when all parameters are valid
    ├── it increments nextId
    ├── it stores the breadfund with correct id
    ├── it sets all members as isMember
    ├── it adds breadfund id to each member's breadfunds list
    └── it emits BreadfundCreated event

BreadfundsUnit::decommission
├── when breadfund is not decommissionable
│   └── it reverts with NotDecommissionable
├── when breadfund is decommissionable
│   ├── when members have withdrawable balances
│   │   ├── it transfers each member's withdrawable balance
│   │   ├── it sets withdrawable balances to zero
│   │   └── when transfer fails
│   │       └── it reverts with TransferFailed
│   ├── when remaining balance exists after withdrawals
│   │   ├── it calculates equal distribution
│   │   ├── it transfers equal amounts to all members
│   │   └── when transfer fails
│   │       └── it reverts with TransferFailed
│   ├── when no remaining balance exists
│   │   └── it skips distribution
│   ├── it sets breadfund balance to zero
│   ├── it deletes the breadfund
│   └── it emits BreadfundDecommissioned event
└── when called with reentrancy attempt
    └── it reverts with reentrancy guard

BreadfundsUnit::deposit
├── when breadfund is not commissioned
│   └── it reverts with NotCommissioned
├── when caller is not a member
│   └── it reverts with NotMember
├── when deposit amount is zero
│   └── it reverts with InvalidDepositAmount
├── when deposit amount is negative
│   └── it reverts with InvalidDepositAmount
├── when depositing before breadfund start time
│   └── it reverts with DepositBeforeBreadfundStart
├── when already deposited in current epoch
│   └── it reverts with AlreadyDeposited
├── when making first deposit
│   ├── it adds initial deposit to total
│   ├── it adds fixed deposit to total
│   ├── it sets hasMadeFirstDeposit to true
│   ├── it stores member contribution
│   └── it calculates withdrawable with ratio
├── when making subsequent deposit
│   ├── it adds only fixed deposit to total
│   └── it calculates withdrawable with ratio
├── when transferFrom fails
│   └── it reverts with TransferFailed
└── when deposit is valid
    ├── it updates breadfund balance
    ├── it updates member withdrawable balance
    ├── it marks member as deposited in current epoch
    ├── it transfers tokens from member
    └── it emits FundsDeposited event

BreadfundsUnit::depositFor
├── when breadfund is not commissioned
│   └── it reverts with NotCommissioned
├── when target member is not a member
│   └── it reverts with NotMember
├── when deposit amount is zero or less
│   └── it reverts with InvalidDepositAmount
├── when depositing before breadfund start time
│   └── it reverts with DepositBeforeBreadfundStart
├── when member already deposited in current epoch
│   └── it reverts with AlreadyDeposited
├── when transferFrom from sender fails
│   └── it reverts with TransferFailed
└── when deposit is valid
    ├── it updates breadfund balance for target member
    ├── it updates target member withdrawable balance
    ├── it marks target member as deposited in current epoch
    ├── it transfers tokens from sender not target
    └── it emits FundsDeposited event for target member

BreadfundsUnit::withdraw
├── when breadfund is not commissioned
│   └── it reverts with NotCommissioned
├── when caller is not a member
│   └── it reverts with NotMember
├── when days requested is zero
│   └── it calculates zero withdrawal amount
├── when member contribution is zero
│   └── it calculates zero daily withdrawable
├── when ratio is zero
│   └── it calculates zero withdrawable amount
├── when requested amount exceeds withdrawable balance
│   └── it reverts with NotWithdrawable
├── when withdrawal is small
│   ├── when exceeds small withdrawal limit for epoch
│   │   └── it reverts with ExceedsSmallWithdrawalLimit
│   ├── when within small withdrawal limit
│   │   ├── it decrements member withdrawable balance
│   │   ├── it increments small withdraws count
│   │   ├── when transfer fails
│   │   │   └── it reverts with TransferFailed
│   │   ├── it transfers funds directly
│   │   └── it emits FundsWithdrawn event
│   └── when at exactly the limit
│       └── it processes as small withdrawal
└── when withdrawal is large
    ├── it creates a withdrawal request
    ├── it does not modify balances immediately
    └── it emits WithdrawalPending event

BreadfundsUnit::createRequest
├── when owner is zero address
│   └── it reverts with InvalidRequest
├── when request already exists
│   └── it reverts with AlreadyExists
├── when breadfund is not commissioned
│   └── it reverts with NotCommissioned
├── when amount is zero
│   └── it stores request with zero amount
└── when request is valid
    ├── it stores the request with correct data
    ├── it increments nextIdRequest
    ├── it initializes votes to zero
    └── it emits RequestCreated event

BreadfundsUnit::contest
├── when request does not exist
│   └── it processes with empty request
├── when contest window is closed
│   └── it reverts with ContestWindowClosed
├── when contest window is exactly at deadline
│   └── it allows contest
├── when caller is not a member
│   └── it reverts with NotMember
├── when already contested
│   └── it reverts with AlreadyContested
└── when contest is valid
    ├── it marks request as contested
    └── it emits WithdrawalContested event

BreadfundsUnit::executeContestedWithdrawl
├── when request does not exist
│   └── it processes with empty request
├── when already executed
│   └── it reverts with AlreadyExecuted
├── when contest window has not passed
│   ├── when not contested
│   │   └── it does not execute
│   └── when contested
│       └── it does not execute
├── when contest window has passed
│   ├── when contested
│   │   └── it does not execute
│   └── when not contested
│       ├── it marks as executed
│       ├── when transfer fails
│       │   └── it reverts with TransferFailed
│       ├── it transfers funds to request owner
│       └── it emits WithdrawalAutoExecuted event
└── when called with reentrancy attempt
    └── it reverts with reentrancy guard

BreadfundsUnit::vote
├── when request does not exist
│   └── it processes with empty request
├── when caller is not a member
│   └── it reverts with NotMember
├── when already voted
│   └── it reverts with AlreadyVoted
├── when voting window is closed
│   └── it reverts with VotingWindowClosed
├── when voting window is exactly at deadline
│   └── it allows vote
├── when request is already executed
│   └── it reverts with AlreadyExecuted
├── when voting yes
│   ├── it increments yes votes
│   ├── it marks member as voted
│   ├── it emits Voted event with true
│   └── when consensus is reached
│       ├── it marks request as executed immediately
│       ├── when transfer fails
│       │   └── it reverts with TransferFailed
│       ├── it transfers funds to owner
│       └── it emits WithdrawalApproved event
├── when voting no
│   ├── it increments no votes
│   ├── it marks member as voted
│   ├── it emits Voted event with false
│   └── it does not execute withdrawal
├── when consensus threshold is exactly met
│   └── it does not execute
└── when consensus threshold is exceeded by one
    └── it executes withdrawal

BreadfundsUnit::isTokenAllowed
├── when token is allowed
│   └── it returns true
└── when token is not allowed
    └── it returns false

BreadfundsUnit::getBreadfund
├── when breadfund does not exist
│   └── it returns empty breadfund
├── when breadfund is decommissioned
│   └── it reverts with NotCommissioned
└── when breadfund exists
    └── it returns complete breadfund data

BreadfundsUnit::getBreadfunds
├── when array is empty
│   └── it returns empty array
├── when some ids do not exist
│   └── it returns empty breadfunds for non-existent ids
└── when all ids exist
    └── it returns array of all breadfunds

BreadfundsUnit::getMemberBreadfunds
├── when member has no breadfunds
│   └── it returns empty array
└── when member has breadfunds
    └── it returns array of all member's breadfund ids

BreadfundsUnit::getMemberBalances
├── when breadfund does not exist
│   └── it returns empty data
├── when breadfund is decommissioned
│   └── it reverts with NotCommissioned
├── when breadfund has no members
│   └── it returns empty arrays
└── when breadfund has members
    ├── it returns all member addresses
    └── it returns corresponding balances

BreadfundsUnit::hasMemberDepositedInEpoch
├── when member has not deposited
│   └── it returns false
├── when member has deposited
│   └── it returns true
└── when checking invalid epoch or member
    └── it returns false

BreadfundsUnit::getCurrentEpochIndex
├── when breadfund does not exist
│   └── it calculates with default values
├── when current time is before breadfund start
│   └── it returns zero
├── when current time equals breadfund start
│   └── it returns zero
├── when current time is one second into first epoch
│   └── it returns zero
├── when current time is exactly one epoch duration after start
│   └── it returns one
└── when current time is multiple epochs after start
    └── it returns correct epoch index

BreadfundsUnit::isDecommissionable
├── when breadfund does not exist
│   └── it returns true
├── when breadfund has no owner
│   └── it returns true
├── when in epoch zero
│   └── it returns false
├── when all members deposited in all past epochs
│   └── it returns false
├── when one member missed one deposit in any past epoch
│   └── it returns true
├── when multiple members missed deposits
│   └── it returns true
└── when checking current epoch
    └── it ignores current epoch deposits
